            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Trust matters when you strap a light-emitting device to your face. The COLORDIAMONDS IGI LED Mask is classified as a Class II medical device and carries FDA clearance — meaning it passed rigorous safety and efficacy review before hitting the market. That is not marketing fluff. That is a regulatory stamp backed by actual data.",
