        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "It also holds CE certification for European safety standards and IGI certification, which is rare in the at-home LED space. Most consumer masks skip these steps entirely because they are expensive and time-consuming. COLORDIAMONDS did not skip them.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
