      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The mask feels substantial without being heavy. The LED array is evenly distributed across the entire face panel — no dead zones on the jawline or temples like cheaper alternatives. The silicone sits comfortably against the skin, and the adjustable straps accommodate different face shapes without pressing uncomfortably on the nose bridge.",
