      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Owning a great device is one thing. Using it correctly is what delivers results. Here are my tested tips for getting the most out of every session.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip 1: Start With a Clean, Bare Face",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Wash your face with a gentle cleanser before every session. Serums, moisturizers, and especially SPF can reflect or absorb light wavelengths, reducing penetration. Think of it like trying to shine a flashlight through tinted glass — you want a clear path.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "After the session, apply your favorite serum or moisturizer. Post-light therapy, your skin is primed to absorb active ingredients more effectively. This is one of the best-kept secrets of LED users.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip 2: Be Consistent, Not Intense",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You do not need 30-minute sessions every day. The sweet spot for most people is ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "10 to 20 minutes per session, 3 to 5 times per week",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Results build cumulatively over weeks, not in a single marathon session. Set a recurring calendar reminder — consistency beats intensity every time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
