        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The LED mask plays well with others. Use it alongside your retinol nights (apply retinol after the session, not before), vitamin C mornings, or hyaluronic acid routines. It does not interfere with other actives — it enhances them by improving skin receptivity.",
