        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Take a photo in the same lighting every two weeks. You will notice texture improvements around week three or four, and deeper structural changes (firmness, reduced fine lines) by week eight. These before-and-after comparisons keep you motivated when daily changes are too subtle to notice.",
            "marks": []
