      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Wipe the silicone surface with a clean, damp cloth after each use. Store the mask in its case or a clean drawer — not on the bathroom counter where humidity and bacteria thrive. A little care extends the life of the LEDs significantly.",
