        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Dermatologists and aestheticians increasingly recommend LED therapy after chemical peels, microneedling, and laser treatments to reduce downtime and redness. Having a certified device at home means you can continue recovery between clinic visits.",
